cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DC, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is primarily focused on optimizing the runtime and scalability of large neural networks, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the placement of operations in dataflow graphs, which is related to distributed computing (cs.DC). The proposed method uses a graph neural network, which is a popular technique in neural networks (cs.NE), and the paper evaluates the method on various deep learning models, including image recognition models (cs.CV).
